import './mapsvg.css';

function MapSvg() {
  return (
    <svg width="90%" className="appear-animation" viewBox="0 0 1367 714" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlnsXlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
        <rect x="405" width="385" height="385" fill="url(#pattern0)"/>
        <rect x="312" y="239" width="1055" height="474.396" fill="url(#pattern1)"/>
        <rect y="56" width="643" height="433.602" fill="url(#pattern2)"/>
        <defs>
        <pattern id="pattern0" patternContentUnits="objectBoundingBox" width="1" height="1">
        <use xlinkHref="#image0_151_88" transform="scale(0.002)"/>
        </pattern>
        <pattern id="pattern1" patternContentUnits="objectBoundingBox" width="1" height="1">
        <use xlinkHref="#image1_151_88" transform="scale(0.00134228 0.00298507)"/>
        </pattern>
        <pattern id="pattern2" patternContentUnits="objectBoundingBox" width="1" height="1">
        <use xlinkHref="#image2_151_88" transform="scale(0.00164474 0.00243902)"/>
        </pattern>
        <image id="image0_151_88" width="500" height="500" xlinkHref="data:image/png;base64,"/>
        <image id="image1_151_88" width="745" height="335" xlinkHref="data:image/png;base64,"/>
        <image id="image2_151_88" width="608" height="410" xlinkHref="data:image/png;base64,"/>
        </defs>
    </svg>

  )
}

export default MapSvg;
